\", \"from\": 1361, \"to\": 1366}, {\"ngram\": \"performance\", \"from\": 1371, \"to\": 1382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some 80 giant screens along the way will broadcast the show, which will include a floating parade of athletes and artists and is also expected to feature dancers performing from the roof of buildings along the Seine.\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1602, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1596, \"end\": 1601, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.892076523280881e-23, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some 80 giant screens\", \"from\": 1386, \"to\": 1407}, {\"ngram\": \"the way\", \"from\": 1414, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"the show\", \"from\": 1437, \"to\": 1445}, {\"ngram\": \"a floating parade\", \"from\": 1466, \"to\": 1483}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 1487, \"to\": 1495}, {\"ngram\": \"artists\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1547}, {\"ngram\": \"the roof\", \"from\": 1564, \"to\": 1572}, {\"ngram\": \"buildings\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The show will be \\\"a large fresco\\\" celebrating Paris, France and the Games and will interweave the parade of athletes, artistic performances and elements of protocol, said Thomas Jolly, the artistic director of the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1835, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1650, \"end\": 1655, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.1655340204020848e-23, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1657, \"end\": 1663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999996392971948, \"rank\": 3.117488714422787e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q625